href="http://lists.debian.org/debian-curiosa/">debian-curiosa</a> 郵遞論壇。</p>

#penk 認領
<p><strong>【Sarge 釋出狀態】</strong> Steve Langasek 送出了新的 Sarge <a
href="http://lists.debian.org/debian-devel-announce/2005/03/msg00012.html">
